{"tid":1809800,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"零售額連跌10個月，2019年11月零售額按年大跌23.6%","createTime":"2020-01-03T10:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T17:14:00.000Z","uid":86545,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1481f5f97a8b6cdab2eec43373354e8b7b8edfe7","tid":1809800,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7kWwXrK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7kWwXrK.jpg&h=ed0438f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9371682ff4765c599671bb63125968f24f0a9b5","tid":1809800,"uid":86545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"本港示威活動持續，打擊零售業，零售額連跌10個月，2019年11月零售額按年大跌23.6%，但跌幅較上月略收窄，跌幅亦少過市場的24.6%。<br />\n政府統計處公布，11月零售業總銷貨價值的臨時估計為300億元，按年下跌23.6%，跌幅較上月修訂估計下跌24.4%，略為收窄。<br />\n扣除價格變動後，11月零售業總銷貨數量的臨時估計按年下跌25.4%，跌幅亦較10月修訂估計下跌26.4%，略為收窄。<br />\n2019年首11個月，零售業總銷貨價值的臨時估計下跌10.3%；零售業總銷貨數量下跌11.4%。<br />\n政府發言人表示，零售業銷售在11月繼續大幅下滑，因本地社會事件變得極度暴力，對與旅遊及消費相關的活動構成非常嚴重的干擾，並進一步打擊消費氣氛。<br />\n發言人稱，零售業的短期前景繼續取決於本地社會事件如何發展。因此，停止暴力行為，恢復社會秩序，對零售業以至整體經濟的復甦至為重要。<br />\n11月按年比，珠寶首飾、鐘錶及名貴禮物銷貨價值大跌43.5%；服裝下跌31.9%；藥物及化妝品下跌33.4%；百貨公司貨品下跌32.9%。"},{"pid":"1f721b7feab80e88847d778b2cadf42804e41f01","tid":1809800,"uid":7043,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"叫差佬同藍絲去買囉<br />\n沉默大多數嘛"},{"pid":"57da2a0629d0d18d0f356130f3040078439ec71f","tid":1809800,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7GrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=04697d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"6827088407b08fc8dd6f1bfe3c733ff129bb25f1","tid":1809800,"uid":28068,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"跌咁少"},{"pid":"fda4d7247017b0e365f16cc309e85e8faf26757c","tid":1809800,"uid":129030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6827088407b08fc8dd6f1bfe3c733ff129bb25f1","tid":1809800,"uid":28068,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"跌咁少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"跌太少了"},{"pid":"91efa95024e9d13d3a1d8b53e795329928b166c4","tid":1809800,"uid":189047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"死黑狗搞到d人唔敢出黎消費又懶落示威度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af6f5a6430c2f8f6124171bef725cfda8fdf5f2","tid":1809800,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"不能接受"},{"pid":"33ebb3a9f6c4c85c6450385714425ec73da19dff","tid":1809800,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"失業了  樓跌了"},{"pid":"70c0c36fddb9b3343a5355d88c22bf8e80d51248","tid":1809800,"uid":76632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"呢個數據同時反映到，近呢半年少咗大陸人來香港shopping鳩嗚消費。<br />\n<br />\n大家要繼續堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"d6976e8be77178499d22e0ec7449c7e74169d636","tid":1809800,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:47:04.000Z","msg":"控制下你嗰三萬隻賤種狗先喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673c99594118e713b7e562797cee1f523de87438","tid":1809800,"uid":269990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"沉默大多數冇幫襯咩？定係冇錢幫襯呀 <im